					<ul class="accordion-section"><a name="Where and how to ask questions or contact us about this policy"></a>
<p>If you require further information about our privacy policy, please go to the help section of our websites where <a href="/Help/FrequentlyAskedQuestions/en?lang=en">frequently asked questions (FAQ's)</a> are answered. We welcome your questions, comments and requests about this privacy policy. If you require more information, please contact our privacy officer at <a href="mailto:privacy@net-a-porter.com">privacy@net-a-porter.com</a></p>
<p>If you wish to talk to a Customer Care representative, please call: </p>
